text: The Tasmania JackJumpers are an Australian professional basketball team from Hobart. The team plays in the National Basketball League (NBL). The Tasmania JackJumpers are the only NBL team in Tasmania. They play their home games at the Derwent Entertainment Centre in Hobart and at the Silverdome in Launceston. ==References== Category:Australian basketball teams JackJumpers
